                                            97% accuracy</li>
                                    </ul>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                        <div class="experiences" style="border-top: 1px solid black; padding-top:10px;">
                            <div class="edu-title">
                                <div class="education-title">Skills</div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="edu-desc">
                                <div class="degree" style="margin-bottom:0;">Languages:</div>
                                <div class="project-description">
                                    Python, HTML, CSS, JS, Java, C,  SQL, PHP, 
